{"tid":1420572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真一問]我哋係咪仲堅持要撤回暴動定性、釋放義士？","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:33:32.000Z","uid":264676,"like":108,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b7c285063c071065ea3905797293e8d537390f","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梗係要堅持喇！講好咗齊上齊落，點可以拋低任何一位手足？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但如果係咁，希望大家深思，我哋可以點爭取到？<br />\n如果撤回暴動定性同釋放義士仍然係我哋嘅訴求，咁我哋其實得兩條路可以揀：<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 打低晒啲警察，武力戰勝軍政府<br />\n<br />\n2. 用強大嘅民意基礎，奪取道德正當性，轉化為行動迫使政府就範</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n如果係<strong><ins>第1條路</ins></strong>，我諗大家都知係冇乜可能<br />\n因為我地裝備永遠都比唔上啲警察，而對方係可以合法殺人，我哋郁少少就捉然後告暴動，<br />\n從過往經驗睇，如警方執意清場我哋都係強弱懸殊，我諗冇人希望再失去任何一位手足<br />\n<br />\n咁如果係行<strong><ins>第2條路</ins></strong>呢？咁我哋近日越趨激烈嘅街頭抗爭，會唔會已經同呢個目標愈行愈遠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋要做嘅，就係令大眾相信抗爭者不是暴徒，迫使政府跪低，<br />\n<strong>但今日嘅一些事件，令林鄭不斷有位入，抹黑我哋做暴徒</strong><br />\n我絕對唔係否定緊勇武，勇武巴絲為運動付出咗好多，<br />\n冒咗最大嘅風險，而成果亦有目共睹：逼到警察同呢個政權一再犯錯，令到大部分市民企喺我地呢邊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但同一時間，我都希望在此提出少少建議，大家一齊討論，</span></strong><br />\n最近幾次嘅示威，都發生過<ins><strong>非自衛性打藍絲、粗口辱罵影相市民、損壞汽車公物</strong></ins>等等嘅激烈情況，<br />\n當然我相信大部分行為，都係對方有錯在先嘅，<br />\n不過呢啲畫面越來越多，事實上會令更多一般市民當正我地係「暴徒」，覺得我哋搞亂社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>其實大部分市民都認同運動嘅目標（80%支持獨立調查、70%支持撤回惡法），但事實上大部分香港人的確係習慣咗和平，而市民係容易因為「畫面」產生嘅觀感，如果因為抗爭手段於畫面上越來越激烈、具破壞力、影響到一般市民，令佢哋定性我哋係暴徒，<br />\n我哋仲點為被捕手足平反？</strong><br />\n<br />\n大家諗諗，點解黑警被全民唾棄？點解721警黑合作之後主流民意企我哋呢邊？<br />\n就係因為黑警行為太過份，啲「畫面」太令人神共憤<br />\n所以同樣地，如果我地好似黑警咁，因為破壞、暴力嘅畫面而喪失民意基礎，咁我地就仆硬街<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>林鄭會嘗試重奪民意，為佢搜捕、以暴動入罪嘅行為建立道德合理性</ins><br />\n到時我哋仲點可能令義士有得獲釋或者輕判？仲點可能為成個運動平反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋要戰勝黑警，就要凸顯我哋同黑警嘅分別，<br />\n我哋唔係暴徒，只係被政權壓迫、愛護香港嘅公民！<br />\n遇到上述嘅情況，或者可以諗下，<br />\n有冇更溫和嘅方式可以處理，更得民心<br />\n令我哋更可能爭取到五大訴求，救到被捕手足<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>以上講嘅，係未必啱聽，<br />\n但記住，幾百個義士嘅青春係掌握喺我地手<br />\n我地一定停一停，諗一諗，<br />\n諗吓接下來嘅方向，先對得住佢哋</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，必不可少</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9d806f37f645e65a1e9e23323c72115d91bc9873","tid":1420572,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"標題好撚想負皮你<br />\n標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd17480507c4ea164733662737e1ceea65a8dd1","tid":1420572,"uid":854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好多人係覺得我地慘所以支持我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419811</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n內有建議做法 跪求賜教<br />\n如果覺得啱聽嘅幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4f4a0793d7f6b1020d372581224895937d6942d6","tid":1420572,"uid":120123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"我真心覺得釋放義士係有難度。<br />\n義士唔係condom, 我認同。但實際上係咪真係有條件釋放到？<br />\n我覺得，可以搵其他國家有咩類似案件或案例去做文宣。"},{"pid":"e1f9f756ef344601935c9f310bf49dc6e810c447","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d478ba08eaa4f3c236be2a2069d0e07a2f7b025","tid":1420572,"uid":71199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"如果改做要求林鄭特赦義士，告左個啲照樣有案底但至少唔洗坐監。同埋都算係實質行動有法律依據"},{"pid":"1d34c0e45810e3cebccf7a646a611909cf5a5dec","tid":1420572,"uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"On9，你不如話做愛，無高潮收唔收貨。<br />\n總之，五大訢求，缺一不可，<br />\n私人加多個，柒婆快死"},{"pid":"0a98d0e799774e5fb9a7687840f0875789b3a66f","tid":1420572,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d24d36bc7efc845b3d8e8c28ceb97f4cf5d7b16","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d34c0e45810e3cebccf7a646a611909cf5a5dec","tid":1420572,"uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"On9，你不如話做愛，無高潮收唔收貨。<br />\n總之，五大訢求，缺一不可，<br />\n私人加多個，柒婆快死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"睇埋內文先屌啦<br />\n五大訴求當然缺一不可"},{"pid":"d8350a2be80d67aad2dc79fa78b2b4ac3a31f699","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d806f37f645e65a1e9e23323c72115d91bc9873","tid":1420572,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"標題好撚想負皮你<br />\n標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"Sor for標題<br />\n但係想引起大家思考"},{"pid":"14aa4a58c0b9a8f94d84d17bf6e7dd3357c51344","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8fefd6f1f4b45d893a122679e5485f2542a6a61","tid":1420572,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:03.000Z","msg":"繼「不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆」同埋Be Water後抗爭新原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420765</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"950d936bf0548f263f2f6e5469c796c8555d5a0e","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"我地唔係真係要做暴徒<br />\n而係要爭取更多人認同我地唔係暴徒"},{"pid":"87e39de8f42fc729c88151e47e538e9a1b201a82","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3f8e779de3eb451cf55fe58183331cf4383963","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a5e6d86f36362512f33b331e6e83f0c3d3543af","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"黑警嘅行為當然暴力好多、過份好多<br />\n但係唔代表我地要學佢地<br />\n相反，我地已經搶咗道德高地，就要堅持落去，以爭取更多人支持"},{"pid":"1ea9150a1aaca34e9638072898acfb40414572c6","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3eda105b04284486711e7b6ad465d259f1828a8f","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18c124f8d6786d0bc9d55b68478b8b42c7f1ea35","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92847080031f2503afb176678274f416744bb00d","tid":1420572,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"同埋想大家有個意識，行動之前要諗下去保護身邊嘅人，唔想再有多個絲打俾人侵害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9993a180dd69e48648ac8982cf069735330a7a5d","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe293ee30bdba2390fa189addc1b757e348a3e1f","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7da9d19fcc55dd2c811068d680e99b9e6ed4a2d","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba1b0860c6856330cf0f07943591977e5379048d","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19e5b2a5421754de3c7b307db5d39858d7fa9ad6","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee7657dfd02c992fbc076170d1215f9f4e03392a","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cde19c8209c37a45dc27e5c97df0503e49b2a89","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"560dc74ccccb23c2203319b7f929daa5a72d8110","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"462d1657858c01106272e67c5c24dc1ac53ab7ab","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04a997d6b4c49a0ae4c061bd46bcca46e6032827","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25398c1cca11bb6226321851a3a57a933580e6b2","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fd1778c5dddd9f2bcb383cd6b21fcc8351fc522","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5046bfef2134ecad89d5f9544dd1700d7c6cea8","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79cf13b8f5b01b02805f6ec6073f0639b6be63d7","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95de565598eb21d936c176bb7f1005b98d7037bd","tid":1420572,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"526bc2824aa7f73c7a1f9bfc